ich, U., Christoph, M., A shift of the NAO and increasing storm track activity over Europe due to anthropogenic greenhouse gas forcing (1999) Clim. Dyn., 15, pp. 551-559; von Storch, H., Zwiers, F.W., (1999) Statistical Analysis in Climate Research, , Cambridge Univ. Press, Cambridge; von Storch, H., Zorita, E., Jones, J.M., Dimitriev, Y., González-Rouco, F., Tett, S.F.B., Reconstructing past climate from noisy data (2004) Science, 306, pp. 679-682; Washington, W.M., Weatherby, J.W., Meehl, G.A., Semtner, A.J., Bettge, T.W., Craig, A.P., Strand, W.G., Zhang, Y., Parallel climate model (PCM) control and transient simulations (2000) Clim. Dyn., 16, pp. 755-774; Yukimoto, S., Kodera, K., Interdecadal Arctic Oscillation in twentieth century climate simulations viewed as internal variability and response to external forcing (2005) Geophys. Res. Lett., 32. , 10.1029/2004GL021870","Paeth, H.; Geographisches Institut der Universität Würzburg Am Hubland, D-97074 Würzburg, Germany; email: Heiko.Paeth@uni-wuerzburg.de",,,,,,,,09218181,,GPCHE,,"English","Global Planet. Change",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-38349097943
